Project Name: Implementation of Infrared Sensor Timer
Date: 02/2013-03/2013
Team Members: Guo Weidong, Hong Wansheng
Objective: build a infrared sensor timer to record time for MCU model car competition. When a car run through the gate, red infrared sensor generates an interrupt to timestamp the event.
Directory:
./code
Open source code for timer module and Display module.
./report
Final report in Chinese
./pictures
Stereographs of the timer.
